---
title: Oven-Baked Bacon & Beef Quesadillas with Cheddar Cheese & Sour Cream
description: These easy bacon and beef quesadillas cook all at once in the oven — perfect for getting dinner on the table with minimal fuss. Add the bold Tex-Mex
flavours you know and love, plus a bright corn salsa and rich sour cream and these will quickly be your new favourite meal.
